xmlParserAPIs/JavaxXmlParsersSecuritySupportTest.java`\n\nWhat changed:\n\n- Added a small dedicated `XmlParserApisClassLoader` that loads the `xmlParserAPIs` copy of:\n  - `javax.xml.parsers.SecuritySupport`\n  - `javax.xml.parsers.SecuritySupport12...`\n- The test now loads the active class from the library JAR class bytes instead of asking the JDK/application class loader for it.\n- Wrapped dynamic class loading with the required Native Image unsupported-feature handling via:\n  - `NativeImageSupport.isUnsupportedFeatureError(error)`\n\nThis should resolve the JVM failure while still exercising the two intended dynamic-access resource call sites.", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0bb5d39a304e23be0169f8f8d3756481948180f769d85fb412\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 1267, "output": 1253, "cacheRead": 46080, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 48600, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1777924289380, "responseId": "resp_0bb5d39a304e23be0169f8f8c224148194b7a1253c3315a754"}, "toolResults": []}
